$pearl_page_rental["about-us"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][vc_column_text] <h3 style="line-height: 42px; margin-bottom: 34px;">Who we are</h3> <strong style="display: block; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 29px;">Chances are, if you’ve come to our website, you’re a successful and busy person. You mostly focus on work and family, and as much as you love to travel, you just don’t have time to plan that much needed vacation.</strong> <span style="line-height: 28px;">Searching for the perfect destination, round trip airfare, or hotel and auto reservation, is a time consuming task and too often your day does not allow downtime to shop for the luxurious accommodations you so desire. This delays the attempts to book travel arrangements and leaves one overstressed, overworked, and missing out creating valuable and life experiences.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6" css=".vc_custom_1503413311639{margin-bottom: 25px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="482" img_size="full" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-6"][stm_separator sep_height="1" sep_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][stm_separator sep_height="1" sep_width="100%"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1503413610385{padding-top: 39px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][stm_video style="style_4" image="507" url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XTDMmcIuW74" height="338"][/vc_column][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1503413593644{margin-bottom: 25px !important;padding-top: 38px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][vc_column_text] <h3 style="line-height: 42px; margin-bottom: 34px;">Meet Our CEO</h3> <span style="line-height: 28px;">Having an entrepreneurial spirit for so many years, I am thankful to have stayed in the race and pressed on towards the mark of the high calling. Because of the direction of my life and all that was taking place years ago, my mind would not allow me to do anything other than doing it “my way.”</span> <blockquote>This became the norm for me and so I went through life with that type of driven mentality.</blockquote> [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-6"][stm_separator sep_height="1" sep_width="100%"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][stm_separator sep_height="1" sep_width="100%"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1501678399377{margin-bottom: 44px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1501677951692{padding-top: 30px !important;}"][vc_column_text] <h3 style="line-height: 42px; margin-bottom: 34px;">Our plans</h3> <span style="line-height: 28px;">Just as many business owners have employees who they hire to help them run their businesses, assist them with their lawn maintenance, house cleaning, and child care, there is now the option to hire a Luxury Travel Advisor to facilitate with travel needs.</span> <ul> <li>At Amber, we start from the beginning and organize every step.</li> <li>Your trip to bring our customers the highest quality travel services.</li> <li>Accommodations, Amber caters to all your elite travel needs.</li> <li>From exotic car rentals and private jets to spa and resort.</li> </ul> [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1501677945519{padding-top: 30px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="522" img_size="full" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" parallax="content-moving" parallax_image="84"][vc_column][vc_text_separator title="Company expirience" color="custom" title_color="custom" title_custom_color="#ffffff" accent_color="rgba(191,159,80,0.5)" title_size="36" title_weight="bold" css=".vc_custom_1503556874231{margin-top: 75px !important;margin-bottom: 57px !important;}" el_class="text-center"][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1501159499635{